reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on November 17, 2020
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Useful for dozens of needs.
reviews.reviewText: I like that these wipes are strong, soft, moist, and just the right size for whatever use one needs them for. I have purchased them, 100 to a box, approximately once a year, for the past eight years. The only complaint I have is that the manufacturer decides to change the packaging on occasion from yellow, to purple, and now to green. Takes a while to confirm I am getting the product I have been using. No negatives that I find with this product.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on March 2, 2022
reviews.reviewTitle: 4.0 out of 5 stars These wipes are strong and wet!
reviews.reviewText: I am a 68 year old woman and I use these wipes to wash my face and clean surfaces. I do not flush them.... I just throw them in a trash can. Sometimes two come out of the dispenser and I just push one back in and close the lid. I usually store them with the lid on the bottom to keep them the wettest possible. I also use the sticky papers that were used to keep the three packages together for an additional cover to keep the lid closed tight. I really do not like the lid on the dispenser but the wipes are great! There is little scent to the wipes.
